  /// <summary>
  /// Anti-ripping attestation event. Desktop emits ONE per track in the same
  /// gabo batch as the closing RawCoreStream, with `is_ripping_faster_than_rt`
  /// = false on legitimate plays. Server-side play-history pipeline cross-
  /// references this against RawCoreStream.playback_id; absent or "ripping"
  /// flagged events cause the play to be excluded from Recently Played.
